<ab facs="#facs_24_r1l15">du in den <expan>nehſt<ex>en</ex></expan> acht <expan>tag<ex>en</ex></expan> herein für rat ʒu vns <expan>kom<ex>m</ex>eſt</expan> . wan </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_24_r1l16">vns ein brıef von heincʒen von Redwıcʒ von deinen <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_24_r1l17">ıſt darumb wır dein red <expan>bedurff<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒe hören . daʒ wır Jm darnach </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_24_r1l18">wıſſen ʒe <expan>antwurt<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd laſʒ des niht Daran tuſt du <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_24_r1l20"><expan>wıll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_24_r1l19"><expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ııȷ<hi rend="sup">a</hi> . </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_24" id="12r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Hannsen Streber, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Hans, wir haiszen dich und gepieten dir bey
                        dem aid, daz du in den <expan>nehst<ex>en</ex></expan> acht
                                <expan>tag<ex>en</ex></expan> herein für rat zu uns
                                <expan>kom<ex>m</ex>est</expan>,  wan uns ein brief von Heinczen von
                        Redwicz von deinen <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> ist, darumb wir dein red
                                <expan>bedurff<ex>en</ex></expan> ze hören, daz wir im darnach
                        wissen ze <expan>antwurt<ex>en</ex></expan>. Und lasz des niht, daran tust
                        du <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>will<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>.</ab>
</div>
